code: @Override public void setBeanClassLoader(ClassLoader beanClassLoader) {     this.beanClassLoader = beanClassLoader. }

@Override public boolean match(MetadataReader metadataReader, MetadataReaderFactory metadataReaderFactory) throws IOException {     return isConfiguration(metadataReader) && isAutoConfiguration(metadataReader). }

protected List<String> getAutoConfigurations() {     if (this.autoConfigurations == null) {         this.autoConfigurations = SpringFactoriesLoader.loadFactoryNames(EnableAutoConfiguration.class, this.beanClassLoader).     }     return this.autoConfigurations. }
